data.description: All the space you need in this  gorgeous two-story home, with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Home features an open concept living plan, with formal dining room, spacious living room with plenty of windows across the back to let in tons of natural light and a gas log fireplace, Breakfast nook and expansive kitchen with a huge island! A pass-through hallway from the kitchen to the formal dining room that provides a tucked away pantry for dry storage. For your convenience the laundry room located upstairs. Master suite provides plenty of space, with two separate closets and spacious bathroom.  For your convenience the laundry room located upstairs next to all the family bedrooms. Large fenced rear yard with large cover patio. This home is located close to the beach, and Cherry Point and very close to the Neuse River with a marina only 4 miles away! Country living, NO city taxes in this great community.
